(21618, 12386, 2359, 1, '你的故事 Your Story', '關於謊言與信任的故事', '2010-03-27 00:00:00', 2010, 0, 1, 7, 'Your lies destroy everyone\r\nEven you love , what I care\r\nLike a mirror in my (deep) soul\r\nListen “Beauty is skins”\r\n\r\nHe has no real feeling of self\r\nOnly pretty words, with an honest face\r\nSomething around him is true for sure\r\nWonderful costumes and sophisticated lies\r\n\r\n太期待 夢遊仙境的 迷幻 夢想 僥倖心態\r\n眼睜睜的無奈 不是意外 活該\r\n直覺 足以相信的虛幻\r\n面具底下 現實臉孔的驚駭\r\n卻沒空等待 奮力衝向未來\r\n訂做的華麗 決定了是否迎向悲哀\r\n靈魂映照 表面美麗空洞的內在\r\n\r\n選擇相信你的美麗話語 ', '', 177, '', '平凡生活 THESAMEDAY', '平凡生活 THESAMEDAY', '平凡生活 THESAMEDAY', 'DEMO', '', 0, 1, 0, '2010-02-09 10:23:49', '2015-03-12 13:41:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
